  "biography_html": "<div class=\"research-section\">\n<p class=\"research-text\">Boïdas the Philologist is not recorded in standard scholarly references. Searches of major encyclopedias and digital libraries for ancient philosophy and biography yield no results for this name.</p>\n<p class=\"research-text\">No specific works are attributed to Boïdas in the consulted sources. Metadata suggests he compiled a single philosophical collection, but its title and contents are unattested.</p>\n<p class=\"research-text\">Boïdas the Philologist is absent from the historical record. If he existed, this absence suggests he was a minor figure, his works were lost early, or the name is a variant of another.</p>\n</div>",
